        public int getMaxWaitInMilliseconds()
        Retrieve the maximum number of milliseconds to wait for a returned element. An implementation may return alternatively Pooling.Pooled.BLOCK_ON_WAIT or Pooling.Pooled.FAIL_ON_WAIT. Returns Pooling.Pooled.FAIL_ON_WAIT.
        Specified by:
        getMaxWaitInMilliseconds in interface Pooling.Pooled.Context<T>

      • autostartGC
